    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lightweight, laminated panels, typically made with a polystyrene layer between two coated papers. Acid-free foam boards are used for matting and mounting works of art. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
